title: LinuxGT
description:
LinuxGT by midfingr.
___________________________________________________________________________________

A custom Arch Linux spin. Featuring openbox, lxde, Chromium and Wireless tools for most hardware.

Featuring the pacbang installer by Carl Duff
___________________________________________________________________________________

Features:
- Chromium Web Browser
- Update and Software Manager
- 3D Desktop Experience
- Documentation to get started
- PCManFM file browser
___________________________________________________________________________________
